data.description: Secluded Estate home with No HOA on 5 acres in sought after Cherokee County. Just minutes from Milton and Hickory Flat. Award winning school system. Three full floors with over 6000 sq feet. Master on main with two walk-in closets. Five bedrooms w/ 3.5 bathrooms plus large bonus room. Newly Refinished hardwood floors on main, new paint throughout main and upper floor. New carpet throughout upper floor. Features include shiplap, hardwood floors on main, high ceilings, and screened in porch. Also includes formal living and dining rooms along with den, 2 car garage, plantation shutters, and gas fireplace. Outside features include pergola in backyard, koi pond, pasture, and barn.
